Seeing the ceiling as if it is about to fall means fear of an oppressive, tyrannical person. You should try to protect yourself from negativity and be less pessimistic. A dream of a falling ceiling indicates that after a long period of exhaustion you will overcome some difficulties in your life. Cheese in a single woman’s dream means marriage, and in a pregnant woman’s dream it means her boyfriend. If a man eats cheese in a dream, he will fail to complete the task, take responsibility, or create a project. Eating cheese for a married woman indicates burdens. Heavy and big problems. As for a pregnant woman, if she sees in her dream that she is eating cheese, this is a sign indicating the presence of a male child, but most often it is a person who tends to stagnate and is not looking for work. title: Interpretation of seeing fish in a dream or eating fish in a dream by Ibn Sirin

preview.html: A dream about a fish shows comfort and a lot of money and other interpretations that we will explain to the single, married, pregnant, divorced, man, such as dead fish, buying live fish, cutting raw fish, cooking fried fish, eating cooked fish or catching from the sea according to Ibn Sirin and more in continuation of the topic: Interpretation of a fish in a dream: Seeing fish is a source of livelihood, money, or an abundance of goodness or profit, if the fish are fresh, lively, and in large numbers. The fish refers to women. A dead fish means hostility and disagreement, especially if someone is seen eating it. Fishing in a dream indicates success and superiority. If the dreamer is unable to catch fish This indicates fatigue and useless effort. Fish in an unmarried woman’s dream heralds the fulfillment of her dreams and desires. It could be marriage, getting a job, or a business. Seeing him eating fish means that he will get money or goodness soon, and the best vision is seeing him eating cooked fish. As for a married woman Seeing fish in a dream is good and money, and seeing a husband giving his wife a fish foretells that a married woman will become pregnant in that year, according to God. A pregnant woman who sees a fish in a dream, and seeing a pregnant woman with a live fish left in the water, foretells that she will give birth to a boy, and there is no indication. In seeing the fish to its place. Female. For a man, seeing a fish in a dream means kindness, food, and abundant money that he will receive, God willing, after toil and toil. Seeing yourself eating cooked fish is a good thing, especially delicious fish, because it portends marriage for unmarried men and women, and salted fish means Abundance of livelihood. The sweet taste of fish indicates spiritual, mental and emotional balance, and eating grilled fish in a man’s dream symbolizes competition, enmity, and the presence of hateful and envious people against him. Eating grilled fish in a woman’s dream symbolizes the envious and haters around her and the stigma of others in her affairs or the presence of an imbalance or An imbalance in her household affairs. Eating raw fish in a dream gives a man good news about his marriage to a woman of moral and religious character. This is if he eats a fish and eats a lot of raw fish, which indicates that he will have many children. As for seeing a man as if he is fishing Fish in his dream, and in reality he was able to catch fish, this bodes well for profit and prosperity in trade, if the man is a merchant. Or success and excellence in the dream of a student or scholar, or to give birth to male children in the dream of a married man or woman, and marrying a woman. Unmarried.Interpretation of fish in a dream by Ibn Sirini.
